Once the decal is applied you can expect long-lasting quality on any hard smooth surface inside and out. Best placement on glass, metal and smooth plastic-type surfaces. It will not stick to silicone and may be difficult to place on textured items without researching techniques.

Fixed on Vinyl is not responsible for any decals that are ruined during the application process.

Vinyl is made in the U.S.A.
6 Year Outdoor Vinyl
Application Instructions Included
Not for fabric. Hard smooth surfaces only.
Waterproof
Not Dishwasher safe
Not Microwave safe
Hand Washes Only: Tumblers, mugs, etc. 
Not for walls: If you would like wall placement decals please message me and I can make the decal using wall safe vinyl.

When applying the decal to a vehicle please wait at least 48 hours before washing, once the decal has "cured" you can go through multiple car washes without issue.

If the decal is applied to a tumbler, mug or cup allow 48-72 hours cure time, mugs and tumblers and cups should be hand washed and not microwaved.

Sizes are shown in the chart in pictures, please measure the item you will be placing the decal on. Once the decal has been applied it is not repositionable.

NOT for use on clothing or plush items, do not put on walls as removal may remove paint and drywall.
